snippet.title: Havoc Fox Kickstarter Trailer
snippet.description:
Support us on Kickstarter!
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/havocfox/havoc-fox

Havoc Fox is now available on Kickstarter! We're asking for $20,000 to fully fund the game and we're offering a variety of rewards for those who back us! Including but not limited to: digital copies of the game and soundtrack, enemy and boss design submissions, and even a chance to be in the game! The campaign is live through July 22nd; any and all support is greatly appreciated!

We also have a new playable demo of Havoc Fox for you to try out! Featuring two stages each for both Grey and Venice, this demo of Havoc Fox showcases new movesets, abilities, bosses, and redesigned stages! Download it today from the Kickstarter page!
